{"tid":687853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那：東江嚴重旱災，供港水勢危  香港水務署：本港水塘總存水量足夠  水塘水位降低係故意","createTime":"2018-06-02T15:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T06:38:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":110,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"81399063ead91f578361cd52de2786cbbd810a27","tid":687853,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"今次東江流經城市旱災，支那新聞好直接咁播出黎：<br />\n支那國開始每日制水<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tbu0f5ot2lQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTbu0f5ot2lQ&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ec733a83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tbu0f5ot2lQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">水務署強調：本港水塘總存水量足夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307967&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=faf962bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307967&h=0bbef414\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307967</a><br />\n11小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】水務署署長黃仲良表示，雖然本港今年首五個月降雨量偏低，但目前水塘的存水量足夠今年用水的供應。<br />\n<br />\n黃仲良又回應有報道指，個別水塘的水位較低是因為署方要為雨季準備，將部分水塘的水位降低，重申只要本港水塘總存水量足夠，供水就沒有問題。"},{"pid":"b1e7f051b5af9dda12d489782d5091794903bfd1","tid":687853,"uid":79563,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"第一次覺得水務署好有霸氣，型到癲！"},{"pid":"922a66f0b88461aab654ab7a0a99efa6893478a1","tid":687853,"uid":40463,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:22:41.000Z","msg":"已經搶定樽裝水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6da123afe497b47c6ff916115bfd008ec592b9","tid":687853,"uid":73915,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"夠全年用？<br />\n咁cut得東江啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437b371852d8a7cff5e54b7c5902d7950f14ead1","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"海水化淡啦<br />\n重東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8ec350891411a005d8a5168c3e596dbeadabab","tid":687853,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"變咗東江屎水喇"},{"pid":"1befdbccfc44eb6f6901e644633dbf73bba27502","tid":687853,"uid":79563,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"437b371852d8a7cff5e54b7c5902d7950f14ead1","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"海水化淡啦<br />\n重東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">水 務 署: 現 在 是 為 發 展 海 水 化 淡 的 適 當 時 機</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/664897/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/664897/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Ftotal-water-management-strategy%2Fdesalination%2Findex.html&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c6886691\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海水化淡<br />\n<br />\n水務署在2008年推出「全面水資源管理策略」（「策略」），為氣候變化帶來的不確定因素作好準備。其中一項主要措施是開拓新的水資源。在「策略」下，香港應開發先進的食水處理技術，當中包括發展氣候適應力甚高的逆滲透海水化淡技術。此外，鑑於珠江三角洲的食水需求迅速增長，開發海水化淡技術不但可促進可持續用水，更有助加強香港和其他珠三角城市的良好夥伴合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n我們一直留意海水化淡的最新技術，並已分別於2002年及2007年完成相關的海水化淡技術可行性研究，確定香港採用逆滲透海水化淡技術生產的食水，可符合世界衞生組織所定的《飲用水水質準則》。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">近年逆滲透技術日趨成熟，海水化淡的成本亦逐漸下降，我們認為現在是為香港發展海水化淡的適當時機。</span></span>"},{"pid":"afcbf6459770cc87f694e8ac6447459e18c39efa","tid":687853,"uid":2419,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1befdbccfc44eb6f6901e644633dbf73bba27502","tid":687853,"uid":79563,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"437b371852d8a7cff5e54b7c5902d7950f14ead1","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"海水化淡啦<br />\n重東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">水 務 署: 現 在 是 為 發 展 海 水 化 淡 的 適 當 時 機</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/664897/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/664897/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Ftotal-water-management-strategy%2Fdesalination%2Findex.html&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c6886691\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海水化淡<br />\n<br />\n水務署在2008年推出「全面水資源管理策略」（「策略」），為氣候變化帶來的不確定因素作好準備。其中一項主要措施是開拓新的水資源。在「策略」下，香港應開發先進的食水處理技術，當中包括發展氣候適應力甚高的逆滲透海水化淡技術。此外，鑑於珠江三角洲的食水需求迅速增長，開發海水化淡技術不但可促進可持續用水，更有助加強香港和其他珠三角城市的良好夥伴合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n我們一直留意海水化淡的最新技術，並已分別於2002年及2007年完成相關的海水化淡技術可行性研究，確定香港採用逆滲透海水化淡技術生產的食水，可符合世界衞生組織所定的《飲用水水質準則》。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">近年逆滲透技術日趨成熟，海水化淡的成本亦逐漸下降，我們認為現在是為香港發展海水化淡的適當時機。</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得係支那唔俾<br />\n整左海水化淡d屎水冇人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c892f758606fae4529e862c62fbee5d85e53bc6","tid":687853,"uid":79442,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"個陣夠晒水話買小d唔係話簽撚左約點都要死d水落黎咩?"},{"pid":"ae2d39f14dbe81051e1017aca549b6aea4ed0c2e","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"樓主篇野我睇過<br />\n水務處都話得<br />\n但政府懶理寧願買大陸水<br />\n大陸啲水一唔穩定二唔乾淨<br />\n你話冇鬼我都唔信"},{"pid":"bebb4a8cb8b8f3d4a27b1f6a26f76e98cdf53cdd","tid":687853,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c892f758606fae4529e862c62fbee5d85e53bc6","tid":687853,"uid":79442,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"個陣夠晒水話買小d唔係話簽撚左約點都要死d水落黎咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"支那人無乜合約精神既<br />\n<br />\n不過香港水務署既潛台詞係：無東江水都唔撚駛驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6510aaa9e2d3ab91d36bef9d3491b1a5758660","tid":687853,"uid":550,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"quote":{"pid":"ae2d39f14dbe81051e1017aca549b6aea4ed0c2e","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"樓主篇野我睇過<br />\n水務處都話得<br />\n但政府懶理寧願買大陸水<br />\n大陸啲水一唔穩定二唔乾淨<br />\n你話冇鬼我都唔信"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"民建聯一致反對海水化淡就知咩事啦<br />\n李慧瓊子話有東江水仲使乜晒錢整化淡廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁有直通車仲做乜要使千億起膠鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n