07:46.000Z","msg":"過幾年先係？你就算沒出街去某些區 都知道香港回歸左啦 你知咩叫回歸未？  即係呢個地頭係中國既 明未呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"回咩歸啫 香港原本就唔係你中共嘅<br />\n係強行殖民"},{"pid":"41c40aa98c0573493db730e69a5f6dde9bf4e3b0","tid":687853,"uid":64716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afcbf6459770cc87f694e8ac6447459e18c39efa","tid":687853,"uid":2419,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1befdbccfc44eb6f6901e644633dbf73bba27502","tid":687853,"uid":79563,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"437b371852d8a7cff5e54b7c5902d7950f14ead1","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"海水化淡啦<br />\n重東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">水 務 署: 現 在 是 為 發 展 海 水 化 淡 的 適 當 時 機</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/664897/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/664897/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Ftotal-water-management-strategy%2Fdesalination%2Findex.html&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c6886691\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海水化淡<br />\n<br />\n水務署在2008年推出「全面水資源管理策略」（「策略」），為氣候變化帶來的不確定因素作好準備。其中一項主要措施是開拓新的水資源。在「策略」下，香港應開發先進的食水處理技術，當中包括發展氣候適應力甚高的逆滲透海水化淡技術。此外，鑑於珠江三角洲的食水需求迅速增長，開發海水化淡技術不但可促進可持續用水，更有助加強香港和其他珠三角城市的良好夥伴合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n我們一直留意海水化淡的最新技術，並已分別於2002年及2007年完成相關的海水化淡技術可行性研究，確定香港採用逆滲透海水化淡技術生產的食水，可符合世界衞生組織所定的《飲用水水質準則》。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">近年逆滲透技術日趨成熟，海水化淡的成本亦逐漸下降，我們認為現在是為香港發展海水化淡的適當時機。</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得係支那唔俾<br />\n整左海水化淡d屎水冇人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"中央有所謂，但廣東個邊既得利益當年唔肯。"},{"pid":"8819922de9b3c5b8d70530b53a78553c01d349f8","tid":687853,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae2d39f14dbe81051e1017aca549b6aea4ed0c2e","tid":687853,"uid":139302,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"樓主篇野我睇過<br />\n水務處都話得<br />\n但政府懶理寧願買大陸水<br />\n大陸啲水一唔穩定二唔乾淨<br />\n你話冇鬼我都唔信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:18:33.000Z","msg":"叨， 班西官 比廣東班官兇兩野鳩到縮"},{"pid":"6ed0622361e51198d79cf05ce599da5fecbe7938","tid":687853,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c581bbaf2e0c46a0d9829bda3479a42bf5773e6","tid":687853,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed0622361e51198d79cf05ce599da5fecbe7938","tid":687853,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"打完個風直頭滿瀉喇<br />\n不嬲都係買太多要倒晒落海"},{"pid":"037fdb8c35b0454d667ee94aeb78542b41de0fba","tid":687853,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"總知比撚左錢 我就要有水用 話撚知大陸人無水飲"},{"pid":"90d30e32643e491cfaa88e383b0c96d5c72d0850","tid":687853,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037fdb8c35b0454d667ee94aeb78542b41de0fba","tid":687853,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"總知比撚左錢 我就要有水用 話撚知大陸人無水飲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"冇錯 用到你東江水一滴都冇你都供落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgm